    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/9112eda65556912e67e718aaf9a47bd9.poster.avif?t=1771776621\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/9112eda65556912e67e718aaf9a47bd9.webm?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/9112eda65556912e67e718aaf9a47bd9.mp4?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一根实时融化的蜡烛。你的任务是探索一系列神秘而富有氛围的地点，沿途解决有趣的谜题。但要快——时间不等人！为了生存，你需要操纵时间和空间，创造性地思考，并利用周围环境的每一个元素。<br>随着你的进展，你将揭开一个充满意外转折、背叛和……蔬菜谋杀的故事？没错！在这个奇怪的世界里，你将揭开黑暗的秘密，目睹浆果的分尸，并体验其他荒诞但引人入胜的事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/0de3d6815c4867f8e170d5f67b751dc0.poster.avif?t=1771776621\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/0de3d6815c4867f8e170d5f67b751dc0.webm?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/0de3d6815c4867f8e170d5f67b751dc0.mp4?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>• 实时融化机制。<br>• 充满谜题和秘密的氛围地点。<br>• 操纵时间和空间来解决谜题。<br>• 带有黑色幽默和荒诞元素的独特故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/07748c8a88a053effb5c48888eb13140.poster.avif?t=1771776621\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/07748c8a88a053effb5c48888eb13140.webm?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269430/extras/07748c8a88a053effb5c48888eb13140.mp4?t=1771776621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你读到最后了吗？哇！大多数人只看预告片。有些人会查看截图。几乎没有人阅读描述。◕‿◕<br>祝你有个美好的一天！如果你决定尝试这款游戏，愿你的蜡烛燃烧得明亮（但不要太快！）。请将游戏添加到你的愿望单。我是一个小独立开发者，这对我来说意义重大。(｡◕‿‿◕｡)</p>",
